I don't think whoever said this was talking about waiters/servers.  He's talking about the coffee shops and stores that have the jar out front.  These people DO get paid minimum wage+.  They are basically a glorified Taco Bell employee.  I pay them at the counter, they get me coffee, I sit down.  I clean up my own mess.  No reason to tip them at all. <p><a target="Varanuss Albigularis " href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46329
